                <h1>Enhance Your Design with SVG Background Colors</h1>
                <p>SVG (Scalable Vector Graphics) enables seamless integration of background colors for web design. You can easily set a background color in your SVG files using the 'fill' attribute in shapes like rectangles or paths. This allows for vibrant visuals that scale without losing quality, enhancing your website’s aesthetics.</p>
